{
  "title": "ISic003033. Epitaph of Konstantinos, Mellosos and Niketas",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/JVCEV98D\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/JVCEV98D</a></div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>+ Τύ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">μ͡β͡ο͡ς</span> ἐν <span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Θ</span>(ε)<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ῷ</span> κειμένων ἐνθάδε ἐν ἀναπαύ-<br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>σει <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κωνσταντίνου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κωνσταντίνου\">Κωνσταντίν<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">ο͡υ</span></span></span> ζήσαντος ἔ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">τ͡η</span> ιβ´ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Μελλώ\n                    σου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Μελλώ\n                    σου\">Μελλώ-<br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>σ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">ο͡υ</span></span></span> ζήσαντος ἔ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">τ͡η</span> ι´ κ(αὶ) <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Νικήτα\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Νικήτα\">Νικήτα</span></span> ζήσαντος ἔ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">τ͡η</span> η´ <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>τούτων <span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">μ͡ν͡ή</span>σθητι <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Κύριε\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κύριε\"><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Κ</span>(ύρι)<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ε</span></span></span> ἐν <span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">τ͡ῇ</span> βασιλείᾳ σου <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>Ἐτελειώθησαν μ(ηνὶ) Δεκε<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">μ͡β</span>ρίῳ κζ´ <br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>Ἰν<span class=\"intraline\" title=\"line through\">δ</span>(ικτιῶνος) ἕκ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">τ͡η</span>ς´ ⸙ </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/JVCEV98D\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/JVCEV98D</a></div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>+ΤΥ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Μ͡Β͡Ο͡Σ</span>ΕΝ<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Θ</span><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Ω</span>ΚΕΙΜΕΝΩΝΕΝΘΑΔΕΕΝΑΝΑΠΑΥ<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ΣΕΙ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κωνσταντίνου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κωνσταντίνου\">ΚΩΝΣΤΑΝΤΙΝ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Ο͡Υ</span></span></span>ΖΗΣΑΝΤΟΣΕ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Τ͡Η</span>ΙΒ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Μελλώ\n                    σου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Μελλώ\n                    σου\">ΜΕΛΛΩ<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>Σ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Ο͡Υ</span></span></span>ΖΗΣΑΝΤΟΣΕ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Τ͡Η</span>ΙΚ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Νικήτα\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Νικήτα\">ΝΙΚΗΤΑ</span></span>ΖΗΣΑΝΤΟΣΕ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Τ͡Η</span>Η<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>ΤΟΥΤΩΝ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Μ͡Ν͡Η</span>ΣΘΗΤΙ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Κύριε\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κύριε\"><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Κ</span><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Ε</span></span></span>ΕΝ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Τ͡Η</span>ΒΑΣΙΛΕΙΑΣΟΥ<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ΕΤΕΛΕΙΩΘΗΣΑΝΜΔΕΚΕ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Μ͡Β</span>ΡΙΩΚΖ<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>ΙΝ<span class=\"intraline\" title=\"line through\">Δ</span>ΕΚ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Τ͡Η</span>Σ⸙</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003033_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; Manganaro 2001, fig.1\" src=\"ISic003033_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003033.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; Manganaro 2001, fig.1\" src=\"ISic003033-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text after Manganaro 2001, with ligatures added</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>Tomb of those lying in God at rest, of Constantine, who lived 12 years, of Mellosos, who lived 10 years and of Niketas who lived 8 years. Remember these in your kingdom, O Lord! They died in the month of December on the 27th (day), in the 6th Indiction.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>Tomba dei giacenti in Dio qui in pace, di Costantino vissuto anni dodici, di Melloso vissuto anni dieci e di Niceta vissuto anni otto. Di questi ricordati, o Signore, nel tuo regno! Morirono nel mese di dicesmbre (il giorno) ventisette. della indizione sesta.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 51.1378 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> 42.0869 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> Rocco 1983 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001619\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001619</a></li><li> Brugnone 1988-1989 360-361 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002120\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002120</a></li><li> Manganaro 2001 131-134 fig.1 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001807\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001807</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"><p>Extensive use of ligatures</p> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
