an>σθητι <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Κύριε\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κύριε\"><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Κ</span>(ύρι)<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ε</span></span></span> ἐν <span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">τ͡ῇ</span> βασιλείᾳ σου <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>Ἐτελειώθησαν μ(ηνὶ) Δεκε<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">μ͡β</span>ρίῳ κζ´ <br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>Ἰν<span class=\"intraline\" title=\"line through\">δ</span>(ικτιῶνος) ἕκ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">τ͡η</span>ς´ ⸙ </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/JVCEV98D\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/JVCEV98D</a></div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>+ΤΥ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Μ͡Β͡Ο͡Σ</span>ΕΝ<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Θ</span><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Ω</span>ΚΕΙΜΕΝΩΝΕΝΘΑΔΕΕΝΑΝΑΠΑΥ<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ΣΕΙ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κωνσταντίνου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κωνσταντίνου\">ΚΩΝΣΤΑΝΤΙΝ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Ο͡Υ</span></span></span>ΖΗΣΑΝΤΟΣΕ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Τ͡Η</span>ΙΒ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Μελλώ\n                    σου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Μελλώ\n                    σου\">ΜΕΛΛΩ<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>Σ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Ο͡Υ</span></span></span>ΖΗΣΑΝΤΟΣΕ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Τ͡Η</span>ΙΚ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Νικήτα\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Νικήτα\">ΝΙΚΗΤΑ</span></span>ΖΗΣΑΝΤΟΣΕ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Τ͡Η</span>Η<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>ΤΟΥΤΩΝ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Μ͡Ν͡Η</span>ΣΘΗΤΙ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Κύριε\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κύριε\"><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Κ</span><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Ε</span></span></span>ΕΝ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Τ͡Η</span>ΒΑΣΙΛΕΙΑΣΟΥ<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ΕΤΕΛΕΙΩΘΗΣΑΝΜΔΕΚΕ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Μ͡Β</span>ΡΙΩΚΖ<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>ΙΝ<span class=\"intraline\" title=\"line through\">Δ</span>ΕΚ<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Τ͡Η</span>Σ⸙</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div>"
